{"data":{"actions":[{"callId":"chatcmpl-tool-9ed151e06f706b7a","input":{"filename":"social_sentiment_report.md","title":"Prioritized Action Report – Social Sentiment Monitor","markdown":"# Prioritized Action Report – Social Sentiment Monitor\n\n**Generated:** 2026-06-18\n\n## Overview\nThe latest analysis of operational records (3 total) reveals a combined risk score of **20** and opportunity score of **16.1**. The records vary in status and impact:\n\n| ID | Title | Status | Impact | Risk | Opportunity |\n|----|-------|--------|--------|------|------------|\n| 19-A | Social sentiment monitor priority case | **urgent** | 48,023 | 6 | 8.8 |\n| 19-C | Social sentiment monitor blocked follow‑up | **blocked** | 22,009 | 6 | 4.2 |\n| 19-B | Social sentiment monitor routine queue item | **in_review** | 11,147 | 2 | 3.1 |\n\nThe **urgent** case (19‑A) dominates both impact and opportunity, while the blocked case (19‑C) represents a critical dependency that must be cleared to unlock further value.\n\n## Prioritized Actions (High → Low)\n\n1. **Resolve Record 19‑A – Urgent Priority Case**\n   - **Why:** Highest impact (48k) and opportunity (8.8). Immediate execution will deliver the greatest sentiment‑driven insight for Growth.\n   - **Recommended Steps:**\n     - Verify data pipelines for social stream ingestion.\n     - Run clustering algorithm on the latest 7‑day window.\n     - Produce a sentiment‑driver summary for the product team.\n   - **Owner:** Growth – Social Sentiment Team.\n   - **Target Completion:** 2‑3 business days.\n\n2. **Unblock Record 19‑C – Blocked Follow‑up**\n   - **Why:** Though risk equals 19‑A, it is currently blocked, preventing downstream actions. Clearing this dependency unlocks ~22k impact.\n   - **Root Causes (assumed):** Cross‑functional data‑share agreement or missing API key.\n   - **Recommended Steps:**\n     - Identify the blocking stakeholder (e.g., Data Engineering).\n     - Schedule a short alignment meeting (≤30 min).\n     - Obtain required access or resolve integration error.\n   - **Owner:** Growth – Platform Ops liaison.\n   - **Target Completion:** 5‑7 business days.\n\n3. **Review & Optimize Record 19‑B – Routine Queue Item**\n   - **Why:** Low risk (2) but still offers a modest opportunity (3.1). Serves as a validation baseline for the urgent work.\n   - **Recommended Steps:**\n     - Run the standard sentiment clustering on a control dataset.\n     - Compare results against 19‑A findings to calibrate metrics.\n   - **Owner:** Growth – Social Sentiment Analyst.\n   - **Target Completion:** Concurrent with 19‑A (within the same sprint).\n\n## Next Steps & Monitoring\n- **Dashboard Update:** Add a real‑time widget showing sentiment‑cluster health, keyed to the three records above.\n- **Risk Review Cadence:** Weekly briefings with the Growth leadership to re‑score any emerging blockers.\n- **Documentation:** Capture the pipeline configuration and any cross‑team dependencies in the internal knowledge base.\n\n## Assumptions & Uncertainty\n- The risk and opportunity scores are taken directly from the `analyze_records` output; no additional external verification was performed.\n- Blocked status for 19‑C is assumed to be due to a data‑access dependency (common in this domain). If the root cause differs, the recommended unblock steps may need adjustment.\n- All owners have the capacity to address the tasks within the indicated timelines; resource constraints are not modeled here.\n\n---\n*Report prepared by the Social Sentiment Monitor (Agent 19) using internal dossier and operational records.*"},"kind":"tool-call","toolName":"write_report"}],"sequence":0,"stepIndex":3,"turnId":"turn_0"},"type":"actions.requested","meta":{"at":"2026-06-18T15:13:51.583Z"}}
